      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know. everything just feels so incredibly hollow lately. like, we spend all this time working, building relationships, trying to \"matter,\" but in the grand scheme of the universe, it's all just static. just a brief, meaningless flicker before we go back to nothing. it feels exhausting to keep pretending there's a point to it all.",
